_sText:
Port of the Quake 3 DeFRaG map r7-menacy, created by r7 AKA Rust7. Small sort-of-strafe map with 1 checkpoint in the middle. Sort of difficult to route but the jumps are easy themselves. Only added 1 jump and removed the water because I prefer the look of it. Literally the fastest I've ever ported a map. It took me about 10 minutes. 

Difficulty: Easy - Medium
Length: Less than 1 minute, possibly around 30 seconds.

I believe the guy I credited is the real Rust7 but if it's not I'll link his worldspawn q3df "profile" here:
https://ws.q3df.org/maps/?map=&au=Rust7
